label: Notebook No.171
description: Belgium. This Notebook is one of a group of 3 (171 - 173) representing a differnt type of Notebook, being smaller in size to others, and with small pencil holder tabs and a pocket at the end (both integral to the format of the Notebooks, and apparently unused by Lyell). It has not been possible to photograph the pocket itself. Coloured image on page 65
